description: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files. It allows developers to create new diagrams and work with VSD, VSDX, VSTX, VSSX, VSS, VST, VSX, VTX, VDW and VDX files on ASP.NET web applications, web services and Windows applications. It allows you to open files and manipulate the elements of the diagram, from lines and fills, to more complex elements, and then export to VDX, VSX,VSDX,VSSX,VSTX, VTX, XPS, HTML, SVG, SWF, XAML, image or PDF formats.
releaseNotes:
This release introduces the features, enhancements,task and bug fixes as detailed below:
   
   Enhancements 
   DIAGRAMNET-50494-Add support to duplicate / clone a diagram page
   DIAGRAMNET-51057-The command button is missing after removing a page from VSDM
   DIAGRAMNET-51422-VSDX to PDF - the shadows are being ignored on process shapes
     
    Bugs 
   DIAGRAMNET-50467-VSD to PDF conversion, the company corporate logo is misplaced
   DIAGRAMNET-50469-VSD to PDF conversion, the radio shape text is slightly up than usual
   DIAGRAMNET-51199-Title text is not aligned on saving a VSDM to SVG
   DIAGRAMNET-51388-Issues with vsdx files loading and saving
   DIAGRAMNET-51398-VSD to PNG - the text position is incorrect
   DIAGRAMNET-51407-VSD to JPEG - the text items are misplaced
   DIAGRAMNET-51419-Shapes are not resized properly in vsdx file
   DIAGRAMNET-51420-Vsdx file gets corrupted after loading and saving
   DIAGRAMNET-51421-VSDX to PDF - incorrect font color of the text
